Version 0.2.0 11 Mar 2026 by Luis Pedro Coelho
	* Add `# GMSC-mapper version ...` comments to generated TSV outputs and
	  `summary.txt`
	* cli: Add `citation` subcommand to print the paper citation
	* Download xz-compressed FASTA and convert to gzip on the fly
	* Use requests library instead of wget for database downloads
	* Fix typo in output filename: predicted.filterd.smorf.faa →
	  predicted.filtered.smorf.faa
	* Fix FutureWarning from newer pandas in taxonomy mapping
	* Remove auto-download/install of diamond and mmseqs; show an error if
	  the tools are not installed
	* cli: Add --version option
	* Validate --mode argument in createdb subcommand
	* Fix inverted condition in contig length check
	* Fix duplicate sequence filtering in filter_smorfs()
	* Fix overly broad exception handling in generate_fasta()
	* Fix resource leak in predicted_smorf_count()
	* Convert project packaging from setup.py to pyproject.toml
	* downloaddb: Add download progress feedback (file size) to stderr (except
	when --quiet is used)
	* downloaddb: Hint to run `createdb` after downloading
	* Internal: update testing to use uv
	* Internal: test in newer versions of Python
	* Internal: use tmp_path fixture in tests
	* Internal: skip diamond/mmseqs tests when binaries are not in PATH
	* Internal: remove outdated installation helpers

